<HEADLINE>
FT  29 NOV 93 / Observer: Room service
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The Queens Moat House hotel in Bournemouth is making an offer which can
hardly be refused; spend three days there at the New Year and get three
nights for Pounds 5 apiece next summer.
Given the hotel chain's pre-tax Pounds 1.04bn loss for its last year of
trading and its Pounds 1.18bn debt, Bournemouth's seem a generous offer. But
