Educated: Ecole Nationale d'Administration, Paris
Academic qualifications: graduated in law; Diploma from l'Institut
d'Etudes Politiques
Career:
1970: Inspecteur des Finances
1981: chief of staff to Laurent Fabius
1982: Professor at l'Institut d'Etudes Politiques de Paris
1992: Renault's chief executive officer, chairman of the board
