 -----------------------------------------------------------------
                     Worried       Economy
                     about         will
                     redundancy    improve
 -----------------------------------------------------------------
April                  41%           39%
May                    43%           33%
June                   44%           28%
July                   51%           35%
Aug                    47%           33%
Sept                   43%           26%
Oct                    53%           24%
Nov                    47%           27%
 -----------------------------------------------------------------
Source: MORI/IRS poll of 930 adults, November 18-22
